ygData.messageBody:
Well you guys will have to let me know how it is... my guild is currently
obsessed with gathering keys but I wasn't even allowed to be in the shaman
lotto because I'm not 60 ... trying not to get bitter here :)

Good news is, Halana finally got 59, and Tani 43 :)

Happy Monday :)

Halana, 59th *cheer* Shaman
Tani, 43rd Bardette
Solusek Ro
